{"tid":1952941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支那輸出獨裁+警暴] 肯雅政府以防疫之名戒嚴, 警察進入社區射殺陽台13歲男童, 向打工仔人群射TG","createTime":"2020-04-01T01:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:28:22.000Z","uid":14918,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8d667a54b084f96222ca321093f4c37c70a4205b","tid":1952941,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:50:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/13-year-shot-dead-kenyan-police-enforcing-curfew-69895736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FInternational%2FwireStory%2F13-year-shot-dead-kenyan-police-enforcing-curfew-69895736&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=0f189de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/13-year-shot-dead-kenyan-police-enforcing-curfew-69895736</a><br />\n<br />\n(以下為不負責任translate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n隨著武漢病毒的封鎖在全球範圍內擴展，數十億人發現他們現在面臨著前所未有的限制。 全世界的警察都被授予了控制行為的許可，這種行為即使對於專制國家也通常是極端的。<br />\n<br />\n星期二，肯尼亞警察向內羅畢的一個陽台上的一名13歲男孩開槍打死，當時警察通過鄰居，實施武漢病毒宵禁，他們對此表示&ldquo;誠摯慰問&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;他們像趕牛一樣呼喝並毆打我們，我們是守法的公民，&rdquo;被槍殺男孩Yasin的父親侯賽因&middot;莫約（Hussein Moyo）說。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上週，在港口城市蒙巴薩，警察向上班族發射催淚瓦斯，導致數百人擠在一起咳嗽並擦去眼淚。 還拍攝了警官用警棍打人的鏡頭。</span><br />\n<br />\n肯尼亞警察改革工作小組在一份聲明中說：&ldquo;如果說這項行動是為了保護人們免於傳播病毒，那這項行動就完全相反了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BqMVYZ0pUBc&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBqMVYZ0pUBc%26feature%3Demb_title&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=5a7c9c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BqMVYZ0pUBc&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mediad.publicbroadcasting.net/p/shared/npr/styles/placed_wide/nprshared/202003/822603990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb